This paper deals with the placement of mobile edge applications, which involves network infrastructure and resource allocation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of blockchain technology, which falls under the category of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper uses optimization techniques and heuristics, which are related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses security and trust issues, which are related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
